{"type": "article", "id": 28910, "title": "速冷水杯", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-30T06:55:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607031503584aDKfFVE5wIgo1Ud.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>夏天想来一杯冰咖啡提神，你可能会碰到以下两种情况：放冰箱里需要等，加冰块则会冲淡口感。HyperChiller 是一个可以在一分钟内让饮料快速降温的杯子，由热变冰的原理在于内部的三段式结构。使用前需要在最外和最内两层注水，放入冷冻柜 12 小时后再取出，就能利用温度传导让中间饮料层的热饮迅速变冷。HyperChiller 可以用来冰冻任何液体，最大容量为 350 毫升。由于二氧化碳会在冰冻的过程中大量流失，官方并不推荐倒入啤酒或者是汽水。这是它的<a href=\"http://hyperchiller.com/products/hyperchiller-iced-coffee-maker\">购买链接</a>，售价为 29.99 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150356lJ9HZprOhFb6gzuC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031503568bw0r5KoTSU3pl14.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150357MSytzQlfGmH9ANa3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150357VYl6X5FC48b9ufWz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}